Package emulator.core.cpu

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Addition
    Adds registers, 16-bit combined registers, and memory locations.
    BitShift
    Shifts/Rotates register or byte of memory.
    BitTest
    Tests if a bit is set in a byte.
    Compare
    Compares register or byte in memory.
    Decrement
    Decrements a register or 16-bit combined register.
    ExclusiveOR
    Performs a bitwise Exclusive OR operation on a register or byte in memory.
    Increment
    Increments a register or 16-bit combined register.
    Jump
    Handles jump, jump-to-subroutine, and call instructions.
    Load
    Transfers memory from ram, registers, and 16-bit registers.
    Stack
    Handles Pushing and Popping registers, 16-bit combined registers, and bytes of memory to and from the stack.
    Subtract
    Subtracts registers and byte of memory.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CPU
    Fetches an instruction from memory pointed to by the Program Counter then parses and executes the instruction.
    Flags
    Stores the flag bits and calculates when they should be set/unset.
    Parser  
    Register
    Stores a 16-bit combined register value.
Version:
0.0.1a
Author:
Daniel Simpkins
